===== FINAL =====

```python
def is_palindrome(text: str) -> bool:
    """Check if the given text is a palindrome, ignoring case, spaces, and punctuation."""
    normalized_text = ''.join(char.lower() for char in text if char.isalnum())
    return normalized_text == normalized_text[::-1] if normalized_text else True
```

